@startuml context
title Forge — C4 System Context (v0.1)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Sans"
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F7F7FA
  BorderColor #555
}
skinparam actorStyle awesome

actor "Developer\n(BYOK)" as dev

rectangle "**Forge CLI / TUI**\nLocal-first Rust binary: agentic coding\nloop with Model Mesh cost routing" as forge #D9E8FF

rectangle "Anthropic API" as anthropic
rectangle "OpenAI API" as openai
rectangle "Ollama\n(local models)" as ollama
rectangle "Local filesystem\n& shell" as os
rectangle "OS keyring\n(secret store)" as keyring

dev --> forge : prompts, approves\ntool actions, sets budget
forge --> dev : streamed output,\nlive cost + routing

forge --> anthropic : chat / stream / tools\n(HTTPS, user's key)
forge --> openai : chat / stream / tools\n(HTTPS, user's key)
forge --> ollama : chat / stream\n(localhost HTTP)
forge --> os : read/write files,\nrun commands (gated)
forge --> keyring : store / fetch\nAPI keys

note bottom of forge
  No Forge cloud account. Nothing leaves the
  machine except calls to the user's own providers.
end note
@enduml
